Abstract Syntax
---------------

Statement ::= Def
              Item

Def ::= List name [Item]

Item ::= Ref name
         Lit literal
         Mix Item Item



Concrete Syntax
---------------

statement ::=
  def
  item

def ::= name ':' itemlist

ref ::= '(' name ')'

itemlist ::=
  item '|' itemlist
  item

item ::=
  literal item
  ref item
  literal
  ref

literal ::=
  ink ws literal
  ink

ink ::=
  name ink
  punct ink
  name
  punct



Lexical Syntax
--------------

name
ws
punct
...
